Package api.equinix.javasdk.fabric.client

package api.equinix.javasdk.fabric.client
Fabric domain client interfaces for the Equinix Java SDK. Provides typed access to Equinix Fabric resources including Connections, Ports, ServiceTokens, ServiceProfiles, Metros, CloudRouters, Streams, StreamSubscriptions, Networks, RouteFilters, RouteFilterRules, RouteAggregations, RouteAggregationRules, RoutingProtocols, PrecisionTimes, Prices, MarketplaceSubscriptions, CloudEvents, and Health. Each interface defines list, get, create, update, and delete operations as appropriate for the resource type.
